ComicInfo.Summary:
Horror returns to Wonderland this Halloween!
As Calie, Cheshire, and the White Rabbit travel deep into the treacherous jungles of Wonderland in search of the Savage, an unimaginable evil from the realm of dreams has made its way toward Earth. Tasked with protecting both Wonderland and the Nexus, Calie will find that her duties as the White Queen might be leaving her family vulnerable
